                <head>No. 14.<lb/>
                    <hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Gresham</persName> to Mr. <persName
                            type="to">Baker</persName>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Department of State</hi>,<lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1894-03-14">
                            <hi rend="italic">March 14, 1894</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Did Great Britain land troops under asserted right of sovereignty or only for
                    protection? Prompt answer desired.</p>
            </div>
